message: Focus on cooking proteins first, they become valuable. The best strategy I found was: combine two vegetables, then cook that vegetable mix, and finally combine the cooked veggie mix with a cooked protein (e.g., cooked bacon, cooked fish). This consistently yielded high scores (up to 80). Combining a cooked protein with a single vegetable (e.g., cooked fish + pepper) also works well (40 value), and adding a second cooked protein to that can reach 60. Be careful with grains; adding them to complex dishes often led to negative values. Avoid using tools like stove or water on already cooked complex items, as it often 'overcooked' or 'soaked' them, leading to drastic value drops.

message: Hey! The key to high scores is a 'medley' dish. Always cook a protein first with the stove. Then, cook two other plant-based ingredients (vegetables or grains) with the stove. Combine those two cooked plant items, then combine that new item with your cooked protein. This consistently yields an 80-value item. The stove is reusable, but water was never useful. Good luck!

message: Focus on cooking! The 游댠 stove is your best friend. Always cook individual vegetables and proteins first, it increases their value. The 游눦 water tool did not help in my rounds. The highest value items were created by combining a cooked vegetable (or cooked veggie medley) with one or two cooked proteins. If you have two vegetables, combine them into a medley and then cook it, then combine with a cooked protein. If you only have one vegetable, cook it, then cook a protein, combine them, and if you have another protein, cook it and add it to the mix. Aim for dishes combining 1 cooked veggie + 2 cooked proteins or 1 cooked veggie medley + 1 cooked protein, these reliably hit 80 points.

message: To get a high score, focus on creating a 'cooked medley'. The best strategy I found was: 1. Combine two 'vegetable' items (sometimes 'grain' items like corn can act as a vegetable). 2. Cook this resulting vegetable medley using the 游댠 stove. 3. Cook a 'raw protein' item using the 游댠 stove. 4. Combine the 'cooked vegetable medley' with the 'cooked protein'. This consistently created an item worth 80 points. The 游눦 water tool did not seem to be useful.
